00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Splendid! This is it!

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:17,000
Vile and evil it is. Hence, I must bring it back for thorough study.

3
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Young master, in our brief acquaintance you were kind enough to do me a favor.

4
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Why not extend your kindness by leaving your head with me? That would please my master greatly!

